\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Oh - oh quite liked her. We weren't intimate with her but she was a good teacher. And - a nice person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 You had a room put to one side as a classroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. As a rule we went into the billiard room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 You had all your equipment and books and things in there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Did she emphasise certain things as important in life, such as manners, tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. Oh she was quite a disciplinarian, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 You always had to be tidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Had to be tidy, yes - hadn't to mess your writing up and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 What about punctuality, did you have to be there at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Did she criticize your manner of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 No. She didn't speak as well as we did. Had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5654282\charrsid5339606 a slight}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606  Yorkshire accent, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Would she correct you if you were grammatically incorrect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. I don't think we were very - I don't think we were very ungrammatical. You; grow up with it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 If you did something she disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Oh she'd tell us off.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 She wouldn't punish you in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 No. No, she never used a ruler on - on us or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 So you were taught for about nine years?
