\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Most people did this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Everybody.
