\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 No. They didn't - they continued with the governess.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 But you and all your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 No. Yes, all - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Do you think it was a way of life because the governess couldn't teach you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Oh no, it was time we went to school and got away. Yes? That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 It did you good to get away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 So you were eleven when you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 My grandchildren have gone at seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 To prep. School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 So you were about eleven and you went to prep. school for two years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 And then you went to a public school?
