\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Would you say going there changed your attitude to life at all?
