\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 In private houses, they were - people gave dances in those days. Oh yes they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 This is what the billiard room was used for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes, that was a good - it was useful for, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Did you used to bring some of your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes. I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 And you'd go to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 Yes, went to them. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4549223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 So you couldn't have been all that bothered about being away from home could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4007407 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620346\charrsid5339606 No, I wasn't.
